OL,4,Cmillion Covid tax bill in Jersey
OL,6,FDeputy Millar said: "I am pleased to
OL,7,Fannounce the deferral of the payment
OL,8,Fscheme to help islanders with the
OL,9,Fongoing concerns surrounding the cost
OL,10,Fof living."
OL,12,FMore than 5,000 taxpayers have already
OL,13,Fsettled their outstanding bills since
OL,14,Fthey were frozen, with around 26,000
OL,15,Fyet to choose how they will repay.
OL,17,FThe three options are to either pay
OL,18,Fall the money in one go, do yearly
OL,19,Finstalments , or wait until retirement
OL,20,Fand then settle the bill within 12
OL,21,Fmonths.
