OL,6,FThe new deadline for making a decision
OL,7,Fis 30 September 2026 with any first
OL,8,Fyearly payments due in 2027, although
OL,9,Fboth these dates are subject to
OL,10,FStates' approval.
OL,12,FAnyone who does not respond will
OL,13,Fautomatically be placed on a repayment
OL,14,Fprogramme.
OL,16,FIf someone leaves the island then they
OL,17,Fhave to pay the money back immediately
OL,18,Fand if a person dies, it will come out
OL,19,Fof their estate.
